{"tid":866212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇唸過其實一萬億可以買起大灣區","createTime":"2018-10-17T16:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T00:24:58.000Z","uid":178470,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c015ea5e03b990e3b301b5118ed2ed7ae90c1f48","tid":866212,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:25:14.000Z","msg":"政府話冇地所以填海，比110萬人住，填海又買埋啲大陸貴沙，投埋啲中乜建築既天價承建商來射錢上大陸。<br />\n其實大陸都係要錢，我地都係要地，各取所需。<br />\n直接攞筆錢買起大陸佢自己發展，反正人地成日貪香港醫療教育點點點，佢哋交稅香港管理咪係大陸起囉。最多整張大灣身分證比佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n機場又可以用珠海深圳做分流，唔洗花千幾億去填（仲唔知會唔會沉降超支）<br />\n係原有配套上改點都好過由零開始。<br />\n<br />\n反正都係利益輸送，不如直接少少，大家都有So<br />\n中國之前都賣唔少地比俄羅斯啦<br />\n到時香港人強馬壯，財大氣粗，係國際上講野都大聲啲<br />\n反攻大陸用錢開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6075628f23d17404fa5c6cdc32835e201e17d7a8","tid":866212,"uid":24045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:31:03.000Z","msg":"同中共買起大亞灣佢啦,又近核電廠方便新香港人用電"},{"pid":"2e4f23874f5a0837f3845ee5983ffb65f27aba91","tid":866212,"uid":24045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6075628f23d17404fa5c6cdc32835e201e17d7a8","tid":866212,"uid":24045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:31:03.000Z","msg":"同中共買起大亞灣佢啦,又近核電廠方便新香港人用電"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmQ6fkw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmQ6fkw.png&h=e5e1b8b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示意圖"},{"pid":"968d04ffa4de4a1c65bd42d183fc26057bfb20a8","tid":866212,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:35:47.000Z","msg":"唔該講一兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a879b08ebfcbab159cef2814dbffdbe569270531","tid":866212,"uid":178470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"968d04ffa4de4a1c65bd42d183fc26057bfb20a8","tid":866212,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T16:35:47.000Z","msg":"唔該講一兆<